content.rendered:
Directed by Rosshan Andrrews.

Written by Sanjay.

Cast Nivin Pauly(Kayamkulam Kochunni). Mohanlal(Ithikkara Pakki). Sunny Wayne(Keshavan). Priya Anand(Janaki). Babu Antony(Thangal). Priyanka Thimmesh(Suhara). Manikandan R. Achari(Vava). Shine Tom Chacko(Kochu Pillai).Sudheer Karamana. Sudev Nair(Swathi Thirunal Rama Varma).Mukundan.Idavela Babu. Aneesh Menon(Noor Ahamed).Amith Chakalakkal.Jude Anthany Joseph. Romanch(Kunju Marakkar).Thezni Khan.Sunil Sukhada . David Blazejko(British General number 1). Nora Fatehi(Item dancer).Jayashankar. Vishnu Premkumar(Uthram Thirunnal Maharaja).Padmaraj Ratheesh. Shafeer Sait(Saidaali). Vishnuprakash((as Vishnu Prakash)). Yulian Caesar(British Horse Rider (uncredited))

Language Malayalam.

Producers Baiju Gopalan. Gokulam Gopalan. V.C. Praveen. Prashant Sharma. Cherukuru Sudhakar.

Production Sree Gokulam Movies.
